reviewText: Not what I expected as far as the music for Christmas. I will do my homework on my next purchase of Trans-Siberian Orchestra.
If you like Trans-Siberian Orchestra - you will like this choice. It has some really good tracks on it that are very well done. Its a Christmas favorite of mine. Enjoy.
Saw TSO in concert for the first time this past Christmas.  It was a great show and the music is awesome.  I purchased this CD after the concert to enjoy their music while driving.
